description:
Create API endpoint for server-side search queries.

## Requirements
- POST /api/issues/search endpoint
- Accept query string, parse and validate
- Execute against SQLite with FTS5
- Return paginated results
- Handle errors gracefully

## API Design
```typescript
// POST /api/issues/search
interface SearchRequest {
  query: string;           // e.g., 'status:open priority:>=2'
  page?: number;
  pageSize?: number;
  sort?: { field: string; direction: 'asc' | 'desc' };
}

interface SearchResponse {
  issues: Issue[];
  total: number;
  page: number;
  pageSize: number;
  query: {
    parsed: SearchQuery;   // AST for debugging
    sql?: string;          // Generated SQL (dev only)
  };
}
```

